  highlighting for C, C++ and Objective-C. To enable this plugin, select
  <guiseq><gui style="menu">gedit</gui><gui style="menuitem">Preferences</gui>
  <gui>Plugins</gui><gui>Code Assistance</gui></guiseq>.</p>
  
